    dc:creator "Stahlschmidt, Peter; Fraussen, Koen" ;
    dc:date "2014" ;
    dc:title "Two new turrid species (Gastropoda: Pseudomelatomidae) from the Palawan region, the Philippines" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.285808> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.285808>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 5. Crassispira bruehli n. sp. 1 – 2. Holotype (MNHN IM- 2000 - 23314), 11.4 mm, Philippines, Palawan, Balabac Island, 15 - 65 m. 3 – 5. Paratype 1 (MNHN- 23315), 11.2 mm, same locality as holotype. 4 – 5. Radula. 6 – 7. Crassispira pulchrepunctata Stahlschmidt & Bozzetti, 2007, holotype (LMD), 17.9 mm, Philippines, Aliguay Island, 80 – 150 m." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/285808/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

